nodes.name: Network Church Sheffield
nodes.description: We are a charity working across Sheffield running foodbanks, debt support, youth clubs and church.

nodes.title: S6 Foodbank
nodes.summary: In 2019 over 5500 people were fed with over 88 tonnes of food being distributed across our network of 4 foodbank sites by 72 volunteers.  The need is great - and your response is life changing.
